Fantastic!!!! I loved this recipe. I'm on the South Beach Diet, so I used a Diet Coke and added about 1/4c Sugar-Free Maple Syrup. It was great!! Next time I'm making it a little bit spicier, and that will probably be sometime this week because I can't wait..

@Jim
The recipe doesn't say how long to put the wings in the sauce between grillings, so that may be confusing.. So, I just dipped them and put them back on the grill on about a medium temp. Don't boil the wings. The sauce dries and the chicken cooks, and you get multiple layers of dried sauce. I actually boiled the sauce to thicken it before I even started grilling, which helped as well I think.
